    "body" : "<p>To be honest, this looks like a bug in maven-surefire-plugin, or at best some behavior change that isn't documented properly.</p>\n<p>I took the sample you posted to GitHub, downgraded it to maven-surefire-plugin 2.19.1, and it works just fine.</p>\n<p>You may want to report this bug <a href=\"https://issues.apache.org/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Apache's Jira</a>.</p>\n"
